{"tid":699903,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［百萬圓桌］ 其實乜撚野叫百萬圓桌","createTime":"2018-06-13T02:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T11:40:55.000Z","uid":39501,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7e833de8310939cf3f1d5772449b93cfc1667599","tid":699903,"uid":39501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T02:07:40.000Z","msg":"見D保險佬成日拎坐個百萬圓桌黎打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話公司請佢去旅行食buffet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇一D又話年薪過百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一D又話年薪=56萬再扣回佣 就入到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁複雜 有冇連登百萬圓桌會員可以講解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8306ed60487cbcfb4e3f9930f2ff9df27b952e1","tid":699903,"uid":77569,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T02:15:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc23c7e67e8467d63e72e8a674b3ec0681fedb78","tid":699903,"uid":121247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T02:15:53.000Z","msg":"恒大圓桌我就坐過"},{"pid":"e33fd0849a8d061447a875218afce61375758354","tid":699903,"uid":44333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:27:04.000Z","msg":"柒野"},{"pid":"21b00bbbd9f3ed604241d30e6a57866176ef1110","tid":699903,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f8306ed60487cbcfb4e3f9930f2ff9df27b952e1","tid":699903,"uid":77569,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T02:15:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:49:13.000Z","msg":"好難㗎咩?<br />\nlump sum投資保單是但都一百萬港幣，咁係咪做八張就掂?"},{"pid":"96eb0bfba97b194d9f4b7329c7681acad42d6e54","tid":699903,"uid":77569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:54:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c7b32ad191da5a64eb643b07a342ac89027c09f","tid":699903,"uid":169895,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:07:48.000Z","msg":"MDRT（Million Dollar Round Table，百萬金圓圓桌會）自1927年推行，是保險業內公認的業績證明，全球多個國家地區的代理會按業績分等級，包括百萬圓桌合格會員，超級會員（Court of the table，COT）及頂尖會員（Top of the table，TOT）。<br />\n世界各地保險代理的每年業績標準，都會跟隨當地的消費物價指數而作出調整，而COT及TOT業績分別是MRDT的3倍及6倍。<br />\n以今年為例，香港區MDRT會員資格佣金要達53.32萬元，或有效保費213.28萬元，故COT佣金即要達到160萬元，而TOT更要達320萬元。<br />\n截至去年8月，友邦香港及澳門有2,648名代理擁有MDRT資格，平均每5位就有一位是MDRT。"},{"pid":"14b9f4145127dd941cc7ed617a95f67c9f1cfb78","tid":699903,"uid":15716,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9c7b32ad191da5a64eb643b07a342ac89027c09f","tid":699903,"uid":169895,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:07:48.000Z","msg":"MDRT（Million Dollar Round Table，百萬金圓圓桌會）自1927年推行，是保險業內公認的業績證明，全球多個國家地區的代理會按業績分等級，包括百萬圓桌合格會員，超級會員（Court of the table，COT）及頂尖會員（Top of the table，TOT）。<br />\n世界各地保險代理的每年業績標準，都會跟隨當地的消費物價指數而作出調整，而COT及TOT業績分別是MRDT的3倍及6倍。<br />\n以今年為例，香港區MDRT會員資格佣金要達53.32萬元，或有效保費213.28萬元，故COT佣金即要達到160萬元，而TOT更要達320萬元。<br />\n截至去年8月，友邦香港及澳門有2,648名代理擁有MDRT資格，平均每5位就有一位是MDRT。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"平均每5位就有一位是MDRT<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f101c7c59675dab15ced942b621c4a3afd90aa","tid":699903,"uid":48629,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:20:02.000Z","msg":"圓桌騎士"},{"pid":"2c9f83b6ad2d9c6ec7288e4409565df55e8beb40","tid":699903,"uid":39501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14b9f4145127dd941cc7ed617a95f67c9f1cfb78","tid":699903,"uid":15716,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9c7b32ad191da5a64eb643b07a342ac89027c09f","tid":699903,"uid":169895,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":